drm/panel: simple: add CDTech S070PWS19HP-FC21 and S070SWV29HG-DC44

Add support for the CDTech Electronics displays S070PWS19HP-FC21
(7.0" WSVGA) and S070SWV29HG-DC44 (7.0" WVGA) to panel-simple.

